{"tid":510402,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"(冇圖)有冇手足記得以前吉野家隻三文魚？？","createTime":"2017-12-26T12:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T16:27:00.000Z","uid":127041,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"69ef0a42f587b8468b3c6922864bc8b5c18b0ed6","tid":510402,"uid":127041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T12:36:37.000Z","msg":"細細個食吉野家<br />\n老母都會加條三文魚兩份食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記得好似都唔平<br />\n以前有得加鯖魚or三文魚<br />\n而家得返前者<br />\n<br />\n大個左自己搵到錢之後<br />\n想自己加錢食一條<br />\n發覺已經冇左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇老屎忽可以講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係定期推廣定出左事cut左？<br />\n<br />\n好似叫鹽燒三文魚？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/26/203440_cb666758067477e1bf6a5bc043ae16bc.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F26%2F203440_cb666758067477e1bf6a5bc043ae16bc.jpeg&h=62329e9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75424ea131f12b271f16ad7188d60edcf78cc334","tid":510402,"uid":127041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T13:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44097ed80daf11b38f3ce65a31b82222b3e2bc8","tid":510402,"uid":15125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T13:13:49.000Z","msg":"好撚好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11305956f12aca3539a5e2c4d357452992c8142","tid":510402,"uid":73945,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T13:49:50.000Z","msg":"自己煎都得啦"},{"pid":"05a075dc197713d21d89db04c29e9d340a51756b","tid":510402,"uid":60434,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T14:09:25.000Z","msg":"急凍櫃拎出黎再放入熱水浸15分解凍都有人鍾意食"},{"pid":"40165ac0500c755ec6ede94bba6611ff38e1ea70",